UPDATE designer_curator_picks SET description = CASE id
  WHEN '1c3dec24-a2bc-4089-b64b-174c67ab352b' THEN 'The Achille LTA1 Table Lamp by Lazzarini & Pickering for Marta Sala Éditions is a masterclass in architectural rigor and refined materiality. This sculptural luminaire features a laser-cut, hand-curved metal plate frame that balances geometric precision with fluid movement, anchored by a substantial base of polished Calacatta gold marble with a sophisticated beveled edge. A delicate silk shade diffuses light into a soft, ethereal glow, creating a striking tactile contrast against the noble stone. Reflecting a modern Milanese sensibility, this piece elevates any interior as a functional work of collectible design, perfect for those seeking sophisticated, avant-garde lighting solutions.'
  WHEN '49c74ef9-433a-4a23-b36a-c365bb1e902b' THEN 'The Elisabeth D1 Sofa by Lazzarini & Pickering for Marta Sala Éditions is a masterclass in architectural seating, blending rigorous geometry with the effortless refinement of Milanese collectible design. Defined by its sculptural silhouette, the piece features a robust frame of solid wood reinforced by elastic belts for lasting resilience. This sophisticated focal point utilizes varying densities of polyurethane foam and expanded foam cushions to ensure a harmonious balance between structuralism and softness. Grounded by a distinctive lacquered solid wood back base, the design represents a thoughtful synthesis of artisanal woodworking and high-performance upholstery tailored for the curated contemporary interior.'
  WHEN 'bc74ed53-214a-4bbc-82b7-be4b21eb2ca7' THEN 'The Inge D3 Sofa by Lazzarini & Pickering for Marta Sala Éditions is a masterclass in architectural seating, balancing rigorous geometry with refined Milanese sensibility. This collectible centerpiece features a sophisticated internal frame of solid wood and elastic belts, upholstered in multi-density foam for unparalleled structural integrity. A lacquered solid wood base anchors the silhouette, while compartmentalized feather cushions with removable covers introduce soft, residential ease to its precise lines. Every element reflects a commitment to artisanal materiality, making this sofa a deliberate exploration of form for the most discerning contemporary interiors and curated gallery-like living spaces.'
  WHEN '485f1b33-fde6-4c9d-aa46-fdee784bdffd' THEN 'The Laviana P3 Armchair is a geometric masterpiece designed by Lazzarini & Pickering for Marta Sala Éditions, bridging the gap between sculptural art and high-end collectible seating. Defined by a soaring silhouette and rigorous architectural lines, this armchair anchors gallery-style interiors with a commanding presence rooted in refined Milanese sensibility. Expertly crafted in Italy, the piece features a robust frame of solid wood and elastic belts layered with multi-density polyurethane foam for lasting structural integrity. Supported by a lacquered solid wood base, the design exemplifies the impeccable precision and traditional artisanal craftsmanship synonymous with this prestigious Milan-based atelier.'
  WHEN '0122e3fc-76b2-4d6f-984b-2dc3f1a55967' THEN 'The Murena Dining Chair S2 by Lazzarini & Pickering for Marta Sala Éditions is a masterclass in structural elegance, seamlessly bridging rigorous geometry with inviting comfort. This primary seating piece is defined by a laser-cut, hand-assembled metal frame featuring a sophisticated curved silhouette and artisanal galvanic brass or bronze finishes. Its architectural base supports a refined seat upholstered in exquisite textiles, ranging from sumptuous Loro Piana Interiors wool to mohair velvet and leather. Representing the pinnacle of Milanese collectible design, the Murena functions as both a functional dining chair and a sculptural accent, exemplifying the rigorous craftsmanship of this premier Italian atelier.'
  WHEN '3be45a0e-b9bb-4dda-a3c1-0dba4bfff3dd' THEN 'The Ranieri T5 Side Table, designed by Lazzarini & Pickering for Marta Sala Éditions, exemplifies architectural rigor and a sophisticated Milanese aesthetic. This collectible side table features an ethereal 5mm lightened Calacatta gold marble top, expertly treated for stain resistance to preserve its luminous, organic veining. The precious stone surface finds a rhythmic contrast in the slender, sculptural frame, which is meticulously crafted from either warm brass or structured iron for a refined silhouette. Bridging the gap between traditional Italian craftsmanship and modern gallery design, this functional artwork serves as a timeless, elevated anchor for any curated luxury interior.'
  WHEN '7c098399-d88c-4240-837c-2ed7fb7d5c9b' THEN 'The Velazquez Side Table, designed by Herzog & de Meuron for Marta Sala Éditions, exemplifies architectural precision through its rigorous Milanese aesthetic and sculptural form. Meticulously crafted from premium solid wood including rich Canaletto walnut and refined ash, this captivating piece highlights a commitment to exceptional materiality and heritage Italian craftsmanship. By balancing functional geometry with collectible artistry, the acclaimed architects have created a sophisticated focal point that honors the storied design lineages of Milan. This elegant side table serves as a testament to contemporary structural integrity, merging timeless modernist principles with the elevated standards of a premier design house.'
END
WHERE id IN ('1c3dec24-a2bc-4089-b64b-174c67ab352b', '49c74ef9-433a-4a23-b36a-c365bb1e902b', 'bc74ed53-214a-4bbc-82b7-be4b21eb2ca7', '485f1b33-fde6-4c9d-aa46-fdee784bdffd', '0122e3fc-76b2-4d6f-984b-2dc3f1a55967', '3be45a0e-b9bb-4dda-a3c1-0dba4bfff3dd', '7c098399-d88c-4240-837c-2ed7fb7d5c9b');